<% tab = '&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp'.html_safe %>
<div class="what-is-era-container">
  <div class="banner-container">
    <div class="banner-img">
      <div class="hero-body hero-content">
        <div class="banner-content">
          <h3 class="tagline-primary font-gotham-bold">
            What is ERA?
          </h3>
          <h3 class="tagline-secondary font-gotham-regular">
            The mission, principles, and humans who power the movement
          </h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="container pt-5 container-section">
    <div class="sandbox font-standard-body">
      <div class="tile is-ancestor mt-4">
        <div class="tile is-parent is-shady">
          <article class="tile is-child notification is-white py-0 blue-vertical-divider">
            <div class="content is-flex is-justify-content-center">
              <div class="era-logo-container mb-0">
                <%= image_tag "logos/era-logo-colored.png" %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="tile is-parent is-8 is-shady">
          <article class="tile is-child notification is-white mission-statement">
            <div class="content">
              <p>
                <%= tab %><span class="font-size-22">The Ethical Rescue Association</span> (ERA), is an
                accrediting body that seeks to bring about much-needed grassroots reform in the world
                of animal rescue. With a team of dedicated volunteers, ERA strives to foster
                a compassionate and transparent environment within the rescue community.
                Through our rigorous accreditation process, we assess and recognize rescues and
                shelters that demonstrate a commitment to ethical practices, responsible governance,
                and animal welfare. Moreover, ERA takes on the vital
                responsibility of educating the public on ethical rescue principles, empowering
                individuals to make informed decisions and support reputable organizations that
                align with these values.
              </p>
              <p>
                <%= tab %><span class="font-size-22">Our Mission</span> is to provide ethical guidelines
                for animal welfare organizations to promote humane and ethical treatment of the animals
                in their care, as well as putting public health and safety back at the forefront.
                By distancing from animal rights activism, the Ethical Rescue Association will promote
                true progress in the battle against the animal welfare crisis that is spreading
                across the United States.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section container-section">
    <div class="container has-text-centered">
      <h2 class="title">Our Values</h2>
      <p class="has-text-justified">
        <%= tab %>ERA's foundational principles are the bedrock on which the organization stands, shaping
        its mission and driving its actions. These values serve as the compass that directs every aspect of
        the organization's work. An unwavering commitment to upholding these principles establishes a
        framework for reform and paves the way for a more ethical future in animal rescue.
      </p>
      <div class="columns is-centered" style="padding: 2rem">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="columns is-centered">
      <div class="column core-value-cards-container">
        <div class="core-value-overlay">
          <div class="core-value-banner partnership">
            PARTNERSHIP
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value-overlay">
          <div class="core-value-banner accountability">
            ACCOUNTABILITY
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value-overlay">
          <div class="core-value-banner trust">
            TRUST
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value-overlay">
          <div class="core-value-banner respect">
            RESPECT
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="core-value-overlay">
          <div class="core-value-banner integrity">
            INTEGRITY
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section container-section">
    <div class="container has-text-centered">
      <h2 class="title">Board of Directors</h2>
      <p class="has-text-justified">
        <%= tab %>At the heart of ERA's mission is its Board of Directors, a collective
        of passionate individuals with a shared vision for positive change. Drawing from diverse
        backgrounds and expertise, the board oversees the organization's strategic direction and
        decision-making processes. With extensive expertise in animal welfare, governance, and
        advocacy, the board ensures that ERA's accreditation process recognizes rescues and shelters
        that exemplify ethical practices and prioritize the welfare of animals.
      </p>
